On Thu, Feb 3, 2011 at 2:47 PM, j syder <scintilla_22(-at-)yahoo.com> wrote:

> Hi John,  Where do you hook the tow straps? jon

Hook both ends of each strap at the hoist hook. Let the strap loops
hang down. Use them to cradle the engine anywhere you feel it looks
good. Might go one strap at each head, or one each at the front and
rear of the block.

John
